  <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style='text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span><span lang=EN-US>Unreplaced insensible loss (dermal and
  respiratory)</span></p>
  <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style='text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span><span lang=EN-US>Inadequate fluid intake/impaired thirst –
  typically in elderly people</span></p>
  <p class=MsoListParagraphCxSpLast style='text-indent:-18.0pt'><span
  lang=EN-US style='font-family:Symbol'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span><span lang=EN-US>Diabetes insipidus</span></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width=141 valign=top style='width:106.1pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;
